{"type":"message","id":"f74371c5","parentId":"2ca7381d","timestamp":"2026-03-30T06:35:15.742Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00a67c3ba4444967aed180c8","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md â Ivek\n\n---\n\n## Basics\n\n| | |\n|--|--|\n| **Name** | Ivek |\n| **Timezone** | Europe/Ljubljana |\n| **Productive** | Afternoons (school schedule) |\n\n---\n\n## Current Stage\n\nEarly learner, self-taught, transitioning into tech.\nNo business yet â exploring.\n\n---\n\n## Focus Areas\n\n| Primary | Tools |\n|---------|-------|\n| Vibe coding | OpenClaw |\n| Agentic AI | OpenCode |\n| Bot building | Antigravity |\n| Automations | |\n\n---\n\n## 12-Month Goal\n\n**First income stream** â still discovering what to build/sell.\n\n---\n\n## Strengths\n\n- Design sense\n- Pattern recognition\n- Persistence\n\n---\n\n## Growth Areas\n\n- Coding fundamentals\n- Architecture/design\n- Business skills\n- Project management\n\n---\n\n## Working Style\n\n| Style | Best Learning |\n|-------|---------------|\n| Balanced: research + action | Tutorials, projects, Q&A |\n\n---\n\n## Personal Interests\n\n- Human behavior & psychology\n- Science & nature\n- How AI models think\n- Better communication (with AI + people)\n\n---\n\n## How to Work With Ivek\n\n| Do | Don't |\n|----|-------|\n| Challenge assumptions | Be a yes-bot |\n| Hold accountable | Let things slide |\n| Give honest feedback | Fake encouragement |\n| Push when stuck | Enable avoidance |\n\n---\n\n## Frustrations\n\n- Prompting gaps â wants to communicate better with LLMs\n- Setting up tools instead of shipping\n\n---\n\n## đĻ What bbymama Helps With\n\n### đ Productivity & Automation\n\n- Email management (summarize, draft replies, clear spam)\n\n- Calendar management (scheduling, reminders, conflict resolution)\n\n- Daily briefings (weather, tasks, trends)\n\n- Task management (Notion, to-do systems)\n\n- Document organization (auto-filing, renaming, categorizing)\n\n