{"type":"message","id":"f16c6626","parentId":"96672816","timestamp":"2026-03-30T06:38:15.388Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d8d7ed7218ff4aa3b37a7925","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"usage: youtube_search.py [-h] [--search SEARCH] [--max MAX]\n                         [--order {relevance,date,rating,viewCount}]\n                         [--video VIDEO] [--details] [--transcript] [--full]\n                         [--lang LANG] [--json] [--brief]\n\nYouTube Research - Search, transcribe, and analyze YouTube videos\n\noptions:\n  -h, --help            show this help message and exit\n  --search SEARCH, -s SEARCH\n                        Search query\n  --max MAX, -m MAX     Max results (default: 5)\n  --order {relevance,date,rating,viewCount}, -o {relevance,date,rating,viewCount}\n                        Sort order\n  --video VIDEO, -v VIDEO\n                        Video ID or URL\n  --details, -d         Get video details\n  --transcript, -t      Get transcript\n  --full, -f            Get full analysis (details + transcript)\n  --lang LANG, -l LANG  Transcript language (default: en)\n  --json, -j            Output as JSON\n  --brief, -b           Brief output format\n\nExamples:\n  Search for videos:\n    python youtube_search.py --search \"python async\" --max 5\n    python youtube_search.py --search \"machine learning\" --order date --max 10\n  \n  Get video details:\n    python youtube_search.py --video dQw4w9WgXcQ --details\n  \n  Get transcript:\n    python youtube_search.py --video dQw4w9WgXcQ --transcript\n  \n  Full analysis:\n    python youtube_search.py --video dQw4w9WgXcQ --full"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":130,"aggregated":"usage: youtube_search.py [-h] [--search SEARCH] [--max MAX]\n                         [--order {relevance,date,rating,viewCount}]\n                         [--video VIDEO] [--details] [--transcript] [--full]\n                         [--lang LANG] [--json] [--bri