{"type":"message","id":"077e86d4","parentId":"b354d2cb","timestamp":"2026-03-30T07:21:26.535Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"We need to discuss adding local transcription. Provide plan. Also need to follow double line break rule for Telegram. Let's respond with bullet points and double line breaks","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"âĸ I can extend the YouTube Research"},{"type":"thinking","thinking":".\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":" skill to include an optional audioâtranscription mode  \n\nâĸ This would use ytâdlp to download the audio, then run a speechâtoâtext model (e.g., OpenAI Whisper tiny/base) to generate a transcript  \n\nâĸ Steps to add:  \n  1. Add a new flag like `--transcribe-audio` to the script  \n  2. When selected, download audio only (mp3/wav) via ytâdlp  \n  3. Pass the audio file to a Whisper model (we can use the `whisper` Python package or call the `whisper` CLI if installed)  \n  4. Return the transcript text with timestamps (Whisper provides segment timestamps)  \n\nâĸ Requirements for this feature:  \n  âĸ Install Whisper: `pip install -U openai-whisper` (or use the `whisper` binary)  \n  âĸ Ensure ffmpeg is available (ytâdlp relies on it for audio extraction)  \n  âĸ Larger model files will be downloaded on first use (tiny model ~75 MB, base ~150 MB)  \n\nâĸ Tradeâoffs:  \n  âĸ Pros: Works on any video, even those without captions; can handle multiple languages; offline after model download  \n  âĸ Cons: Slower (depends on audio length and model size), requires extra disk space and compute, potential APIâstyle latency if we ever switch to a remote service  \n\nâĸ If youâd like, I can:  \n  - Sketch the changes to `youtube_search.py` and update `SKILL.md` with instructions  \n  - Or first test a quick proofâofâcommand to see if Whisper works in this environment  \n\nLet me know how youâd like to proceed (e.g., âgo ahead and add the featureâ, âjust show me the diffâ, or âletâs test Whisper firstâ).  \n\nNO_REPLY"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b","usage":{"input":68363,"output":462,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68825,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774855266976,"responseId":"chatcmpl-86eba60d2e95ef74"}}
